entries.s_81: Thanks again for saving our hides earlier.
entries.s_83: We made it. You have done well. It looks like we are out of trouble. I don't know how to thank you but maybe this will help expess our gratitude.
entries.s_85: We are not out of the woods yet. More attackers are reported to be coming in. Get ready to throw them back.
entries.s_87: So are you here from Ssiksik to help us out?
entries.s_89: Yes, I have come to rescue you.
entries.s_91: Great. I am not sure how you managed to make it in but we are surrounded. We managed to fight off the initial attack but I don't think we can hold out for much longer. Those Wookiees have been attacking us every few moment. Get ready because my scouts report they are massing for another attack.
entries.s_93: Not now. I am sort of in the middle of something.
